snippet.title: StoneLoops! of Jurassica Trailer
snippet.description:
StoneLoops! of Jurassica is an amazingly dynamic puzzle-arcade game set in the prehistoric world of Jurassica. Thanks to unique gameplay mechanics and non-stop action, it's bound to please even the most selective gamers.

Official website: http://stoneloops.com/

More Games:
http://codeminion.com/
http://gameclubcafe.com/
